Title: One-dimensional Dirac oscillator in a thermal bath
Authors: M. H. Pacheco, R. R. Landim, and C. A. S. Almeida
Comments: 4 pages, 3 figures, to appear in Physics Letters A
\\
  We analyze the one-dimensional Dirac oscillator in a thermal bath. We found
that the heat capacity is two times greater than the heat capacity of the
one-dimensional harmonic oscillator for higher temperatures.
